text: Anđelko Rističević (born 23 December 1985) is a Serbian long distance runner who specialises in the marathon. He competed in the men's marathon event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Serbian male long-distance runners Category:Serbian male marathon runners Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic athletes of Serbia
